wXkoYIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=55b1784b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n不過<strong><ins>資助</ins></strong>得 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">UGC 八大</span></span> + <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公帑資助 HKAPA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港科技大學 HKUST<br />\n香港大學 HKU<br />\n香港中文大學 CUHK<br />\n香港理工大學 PolyU<br />\n香港教育大學 EdUHK<br />\n嶺南大學 LU<br />\n香港浸會大學 HKBU<br />\n香港城市大學 CityU<br />\n<br />\n香港演藝學院 HKAPA</span><br />\n<br />\n香港公開大學 OUHK<br />\n<br />\n香港樹仁大學 Hong Kong Shue Yan University<br />\n東華學院 Tung Wah College<br />\n珠海學院 Chu Hai College<br />\n明愛專上學院 Caritas Institute of Higher Education<br />\n香港能仁專上學院 Hong Kong Nang Yan College of Higher Education<br />\n恒生管理學院 Hang Seng Management College<br />\n明德學院 Centennial College<br />\n宏恩基督教學院 Gratia Christian College<br />\n港專學院 Hong Kong College of Technology<br />\n職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"謹此補充薛家宴洗板<br />\n<br />\n政府政策好清楚: 資助院校資助係院校層面<br />\n<br />\n自資院校資助係課程層面，同埋近年開始有類似OU一直都有的不定期撥款<br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學學術流程和自資院校不一<br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學升格要求同自資院校唔同<br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學對畢業生英文有一定要求，嶺南唔合教資會質保局要求，就要新增IELTS有6.5分先可以畢業的要求，OU經歷甘多次五年一度的評審，學評局幾時有過問學生英文水平，特別係DL<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170226/bkn-20170226095130763-0226_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170226%2Fbkn-20170226095130763-0226_00822_001.html&d=OKhsXWmyEKM7vwdGwXkoYIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=816a0511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170226/bkn-20170226095130763-0226_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學人均成本係20萬，自資院校為3-6萬<br />\n<br />\n不論是否自資，以同一類型課程比，教資會資助大學人均成本必定高於自資院校，所以張Cert含金量已經唔同，亦都解釋左貼解幾年入面自資院校學額可以升幾倍，係因為真係無勿控制，成本考慮不多之餘，學額的增加同新認可專上學院的註冊門檻太低、限制太少，0收生都唔洗退場(中止營辦資格)，係台灣，註冊率不足60%，人數不足3000人的大專院校已經要退場轉型<br />\n<br />\n以城大所謂自資獸醫做例子，成本35萬，一年收12萬，其餘只能用捐款補貼<a href=\"https://jump.mingpao.com/resources/detail/20170814/s00012/1502677303702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjump.mingpao.com%2Fresources%2Fdetail%2F20170814%2Fs00012%2F1502677303702&d=OKhsXWmyEKM7vwdGwXkoYIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6242b516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjump.mingpao.com%2Fresources%2Fdetail%2F20170814%2Fs00012%2F1502677303702&h=9e928458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jump.mingpao.com/resources/detail/20170814/s00012/1502677303702</a><br />\n<br />\n所以自資院校係政府角度，是更加容易靈活地因應市場需要，補充資助院校的不足，因為佢地的要求、成本無甘高，基本上可以亂開，例如THEI Civil的學額可收係HKU+POLYU+?的總和<br />\n<br />\n甘就可以順便訓練廉價勞工，但則持有較少人力需求的考慮<br />\n<br />\n自資院校可以賺錢，甚至用黎派股息，學生交學費，有幾多用係學生身上，自己知自已事，所以用錢的靈話性係比較高的"},{"pid":"f0cb7caf825cad7e6bf8e676abb2955b5592bef9","tid":736922,"uid":40286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:26:23.000Z","msg":"我都有樹仁新傳17分offer 但明明我冇in呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好 依家係驚自己英文冇3/唔夠17分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e84bba774ce91891c5ba71889869c177cee7a7","tid":736922,"uid":83241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"珠海真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恆大 樹中新傳都ok既"},{"pid":"404411b2ccbc9410111df60b654707cebf1f5c11","tid":736922,"uid":138068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0cb7caf825cad7e6bf8e676abb2955b5592bef9","tid":736922,"uid":40286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:26:23.000Z","msg":"我都有樹仁新傳17分offer 但明明我冇in呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好 依家係驚自己英文冇3/唔夠17分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T